room_title: Escape room "Stewie's Bedroom" by The Door Escape Room in Charlotte
room_address: 204 W Woodlawn Rd. Suite D1 Charlotte, NC 28217
room_description:
A toddler with plans for world domination - that's pretty normal - right? Mensa card carrying Stewie seems to lead the average toddler life by day - he plays with toys, likes to color, and enjoys cartoons. By night - he escapes to his hidden lair where he is secretly plotting to take over the world!
Your job is to sneak into his room, while he is at daycare, and determine what his plans are. Where will it happen? When will it happen? Make sure you escape out with the plans in 60 minutes before he gets back.
